metadata.name: Substance #01. Timpano Lamp
metadata.description:
Artist: Andres Patricio

Technique: Photogrammetry

File: Interactive GLB - 48MB

Edition: 1/1

Additional Information: 
Substance might mean a physical material from which something is made or even some essential nature. Both those meanings might as well be related to this collection of interactive 3D sculptures and objects that were made into digital form using a technique called Photogrammetry, in which their physical counterparts were scanned and then the digital pieces created.
